{"tid":956234,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"阿媽病到死死下 家姐仲掛住搵私己錢唔返屋企 之後仲上網唱我","createTime":"2018-12-26T06:08:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T16:57:14.000Z","uid":1303,"like":203,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3749cde7e8868a62110fc6bbc24c2d7022ae046e","tid":956234,"uid":1303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"千字文廢事打啦<br />\n<br />\nIn short <br />\n<br />\n細妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己有生意仲7x24 照顧老母。只係聖誕節行開兩日就比家姐開post唱衰。<br />\n<br />\n家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n星期一至五翻工搵錢自己儲起，因為知道無個錢旁身第日仆街。就叫呀妹7x24睇老母，唔鳩理個妹無晒時間翻正職。仲佔埋道德高地，屌鳩呀妹聖誕節行開左兩日陪男朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 細妹<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家姐"},{"pid":"9c0b4a9f58c41ef0c01f4688688520237531c60a","tid":956234,"uid":191352,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adb92e39a8b748ea9ae0c0cc1b84731e0763331d","tid":956234,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"唉 兩個我要曬 打和super"},{"pid":"9a492186347d6184f5d65fee6065a12c37392170","tid":956234,"uid":1303,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/955914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/955914</a><br />\n<br />\n#263 同 #265 兩個on9 仔就最撚點題<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個咩鳩漁夫之寶<br />\n又識得笑鳩人聖誕無出街，又on on 99屌呀妹聖誕出左街唔理老母<br />\n<br />\n完美示範左最垃圾個班00後會員可以有幾on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /